// Archipelago quest-completion reward pool. See docs/goals-and-checks.md
// "Feature 2" for the design. Static data, one row per (category, item) option;
// min_level is checked against the category's governing stat (or %qp for cash)
// at roll time in ap_rewards.rs2 - rolling weights toward the top of the
// player's qualifying range. Pools are illustrative starting sets, meant to
// grow from playtesting like every other randomizer pool in this repo.

// ---- armour (defence) ----
[ap_reward_armour_bronze_platebody]
