// ---- checks-and-unlocks.md expansion (2026-07-15): xp drop, 3 supply
// categories, keepsakes, quest-gated gear. xp is a code-only category (see
// ap_rewards.rs2's ~ap_grant_xp_reward), no dbrows for it.
//
// Quest-critical scan (loadQuestCriticalItems() idiom - grep quest scripts
// for inv_total(inv|bank, X) / inv_del(inv|bank, X) for every item added
// below) flagged these; all reviewed and kept (fetch-step/duplicate/flavor-
// text only, none skip a quest's core mechanic):
//   - excalibur: arthur_journal.rs2 checks inv_total(inv, excalibur) as its
//     Merlin's Crystal fetch-step gate - additive-only, can't brick, flagged
//     on purpose per the design doc (ship it anyway).
//   - vial_water, eye_of_newt, limpwurt_root: ordinary ingredient
//     fetch-step checks (ogre potion brewing, Hetty, Winelda) - a spare
//     copy just skips a fetch, not a puzzle.
//   - needle, thread, leather: Elemental Workshop / Waterfall Quest common
//     tool/material possession checks - consumed as ordinary crafting
//     inputs, not a quest-unique crafted item.
//   - bow_string, gold_bar: alternate-ingredient/smithing-recipe checks
//     (Waterfall Quest, Viking quest, Legends' golden bowl minigame) -
//     ordinary consumable inputs, not a completion gate.
//   - steel_gauntlets: verified against quest_crest.rs2 - the quest ITSELF
//     grants a pair on completion (`inv_add(inv, steel_gauntlets, 1)` in
//     `[queue,crest_complete]`); the three brothers' dialogue checks only
//     unlock post-completion (gated on %crestquest = ^crest_complete, not
//     on item possession), so an early spare changes nothing about
//     sequence - it's a duplicate of what the quest always hands you.
//   - klanks_gauntlets, antidragonbreathshield: both checks are pure
//     journal/dialogue flavor-text branches ("you already have this" vs.
//     "you should ask for one"), not completion gates.
// dramen_staff and any silverlight_key_*/ibandoll-family items stay
// excluded per the design doc (dramen_staff IS Lost City's completion
// mechanic).

// ---- xp: see ap_rewards.rs2 ~ap_grant_xp_reward - no dbrows, code-only ----

